com.netflix.imflibrary.st2067_2

Class IMPDelivery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.imflibrary.st2067_2.IMPDelivery

  • @Immutable
public final class IMPDelivery
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the concept of an IMF delivery as defined in Section 8 of st2067-2:2015. Informally, an IMF delivery corresponds to a single AssetMap document and one or more Interoperable Master Packages.
